properties.Name: PersonalLineOfCreditStatus
properties.Description:
The status of the personal line of credit as of the associated period.

Ex:
CURRENT
Line Of Credit payments are current and paid.

DELINQUENT
Line Of Credit payments are delinquent or unpaid.

IN-DEFAULT
The Line Of Credit is in default due to unpaid payments or failure to comply with the terms and conditions of the Line Of Credit.

Columns.Name: LineOfCreditStatusNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the associated line of credit status.

Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Line Of Credit Status Type.
